.TH "rpc_update_rtt" 9 "rpc_update_rtt" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
rpc_update_rtt \- Update an RPC RTT estimator context
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" rpc_update_rtt
.BI "(struct rpc_rtt *rt "  ","
.BI "unsigned int timer "  ","
.BI "long m "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "rt" 12
context to update
.IP "timer" 12
timer array index (request type)
.IP "m" 12
recent actual RTT, in jiffies
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
NB: When computing the smoothed RTT and standard deviation,
be careful not to produce negative intermediate results.
